1:01:25.848 --> 1:01:26.683
What?

1:01:28.551 --> 1:01:30.653
Gary, I don't have time for it now, buddy.

1:01:31.754 --> 1:01:32.588
Kinda busy here.

1:01:34.190 --> 1:01:36.592
Have Grant duty, he's at the house.

1:01:36.592 --> 1:01:39.328
