1:02:05.088 --> 1:02:08.091
(gunshots blasting)

1:02:09.892 --> 1:02:12.895
(engine sputtering)

1:02:20.903 --> 1:02:22.238
Fucking perfect.

1:02:26.409 --> 1:02:28.778
